{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75ced148fd","title":"对湖南文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8cf7e4c99f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"75ced148fd"}],"tags":[{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"471a503675","name":"张春桥","type":"人物"},{"id":"b42d1ed230","name":"华国锋","type":"人物"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e1397e909a","name":"杨成武","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4b13ff5f30","type":"title","text":"对湖南文化大革命的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"b126229b86","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到湘潭问题，谈到湘潭有不少工人是受蒙蔽的，解放军立足于政治攻势，湘潭造反派在长沙集中学习后，回去按政策办事时）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"0741197b64","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：湘潭的经验很好。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"fdbb402c27","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这样多的产业工人，不会一辈子保皇，要正确对待，至于他们的头头，靠下面自己起来造反。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"14652eecdc","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到常德和安江问题时，汇报了这些地方保守派爆动农民，进城打造反派时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"d7e06212a5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：打打也好，受受教育嘛，许多农民不容易进城，现在是十五个工分，还有三十个工分，有的是抽签去打，有的是二元钱一天，有的是打一仗一百元钱，打死了给一百元钱，没打死也给一百元钱。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"e0318540e6","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到泥木工人的斗争情况时）","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"9c6d5eaa3c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：泥木工人有些行会思想，怕乡里人进城，那时候入会每个人要交六块大洋。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"7dfacf0da4","type":"paragraph","text":"[I11967年9月18日，毛泽东在长沙接见了湖南省革筹小组黎源、华国锋、章伯森，陪同接见的有杨成武、张春桥、汪东兴、余立金。这是毛泽东在听取湖南省革筹小组的汇报时，对湖南省无产阶级文化大革命的指示。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"9eb3c229b5","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到内战问题，有人反映有的组织大，认为人多就要以它为中心时）","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"ff6a61c407","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那也不一定。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"e8e19500e5","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到抢枪时）","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"b3b388911f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：抢枪把你们吓得不得了，名义上是抢的，实际上是发的，政治干校就把枪发给造反派了嘛。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"b523e34502","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到解放军下工厂，造反派对解放军很好，给解放军作报告，武装保护解放军，解放军战士给造反派讲三大纪律八项注意，与造反派加深了感情时）","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"aa49bf7c62","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这也是一个经验。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"e616692440","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到极“左”思潮时","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"a4a2b2c518","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：有几条标语，不要紧嘛，要他多出来一点嘛，群众会起来批判，你们不要抓人。","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"11be7d25bc","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到接待站把一些受蒙蔽的群众集中学习时）","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"5b90e23375","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：光他们学习不行，也叫造反派学习嘛！不然回去不好混","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"2befccd66f","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到“高司”问题时）","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"e532017181","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：“高可”还给我发了不少电报，发到上海，由张春桥转","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"b261adb766","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不是还有个姓方的吗","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"157ac974ac","type":"paragraph","text":"（当有人汇报群众不同意方达到革筹小组时","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"1f4f9c8f8e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：等一段嘛。","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"6cc2734255","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到军队有一段不能拿枪时）","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"1e1a15780b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：解放军有“五不”了。","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"1effd23620","type":"paragraph","text":"（当有人请示解放军游行可不可以拿枪时）","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"5ad9e4944b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：开大会军队可以武装参加。","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"95e7d2c064","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到军区问题时","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"29559aeece","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：过去军区派巡逻队摩托车出去，被拦住，没有威信嘛。现在口口军组织巡逻队，很好嘛。口口军是大军嘛。","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"ef0f71c78c","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到军区开展四天，军区招待所也开展四大，内部几个组织意见分政，大师傅不做饭了时）","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"eacf8068e4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：大师傅也是不好的。","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"29e1d4d5e3","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到火车不通时）","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"a45a3c73b0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不通的反面就是通，社会上和内部都有压力","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"5721cddbe0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那一年我到湘潭，地委有个王治国，现在他在哪里","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"33f48ee469","type":"paragraph","text":"华国锋：在长沙，被斗得很厉害。","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"2ce700f9d2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：为什么要斗得那么厉害呢？我知道他身体很不好嘛！他有高血压。","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"7bb7574cd2","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到军区犯了错误，影响军分区，也影响到县人武部，省委、省人委，地专、市机关瘫疫了时）","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"ea63cfe94e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：中央农业部、农垦部不起作用了，气象局还起带头作用，宣传部、文化部也不起作用了，不是工厂还在生产，农民还在种田嘛！","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"3c2437b7a7","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥（以下简称张）：过去搞精简，搞了几年都搞不动，现在这证明以后可以大精简。","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"35cc7ddf6f","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到公检法的问题时","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"ed4592fd96","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：过去好像没有公检法就不得了，我一听说公检法跨台了","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"589e20215f","type":"subtitle","text":"我很高兴。","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"21a286a742","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到干部问题时）","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"7a886db3fb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：清理干部要搞群众运动，这样多的军分区、武装部，不是文化大革命是搞不动的。过去这些人是老革命、老资格，谁也搞不动他。过去地方的觉政机关没有枪，就靠军事机关","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"cc19cd7226","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：最后归结起来，于部大多数是好的，我们要团结大多数，包括犯错误尚群众作了检讨的。除了极少数坏人，打击面太宽了不好。","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"9dbeca0829","type":"paragraph","text":"（谈到犯过错误的干部进行训练时）","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"a44ce36cae","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：军队的、党的机关都要训，不光是犯过错误的，没有犯错误的也参加，还要吸收红卫兵参加，要帮助他们学习。","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"665fe16847","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到湖南的“红旗军”问题时）","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"e11fa1406e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：再研究一下嘛，看看再说嘛，天下的事不要那么怕，先恢复了再说嘛。","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"ba7e166adb","type":"paragraph","text":"张：林彪同志去年批过一个文件，指出荣复、转退军人不要单独成立组织，应说服他们，现在搞大联合，与别的组织结合，或参加别的组织。","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"ddd64fd1ae","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到湘潭成立临时领导小组时）","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"34a1184c19","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：临时领导小组在九、十月份要搞起来。","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"0175865565","type":"paragraph","text":"张：江西也成立了临时领导小组，驻军召开了全省会议，情况很好。","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"07dc1cfeea","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：开会也是训练。","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"3f4202ebf9","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到天联合问题，左派内部加强团结问题时）","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"9130300e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：都要作自我批评，都要少讲别人的缺点，不要把矛头指向对方。过去我们有个经验，过去军队和地方的关系，军队提出拥政爱民，地方提出拥军优属，军队带头作自我批评，两方面的关系搞得很好嘛！","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"6c612c76ac","type":"paragraph","text":"张：主席语录中有这么一段。","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"1ca07183de","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：两派都是工人，一派造反，一派保守。保守是上头有人蒙蔽他们。对受蒙蔽的群众，不能压，越压越反抗。我们也是蒋介石压出来的，大革命后我们只几方人，蒋介石压我们，我们就有希望了，一压就压出三十万红军，三十万党员。后来是自己犯了错误，才有二万五千里长征","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"7c2b84ec8c","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到拿枪时）","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"5b936c4034","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：抢枪不要怕，民兵就有口口万条枪。","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"b83c32a877","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到长沙的确堡工事时）","index":61,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"0b3f526d74","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不放心就保存一个时期嘛。","index":62,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"},{"id":"5dbca3d393","type":"paragraph","text":"杨成武：水泥的不要拆，也是一个备战。","index":63,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd"}],"page":{"id":"3ac3ea1428","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"75ced148fd","start":82,"end":86}}}},"__N_SSG":true}